history.content:
Hello Everyone, 

I just finished my freshman year, I am intending on majoring in CS.

A few weeks ago, I participated in a hackathon organized by MIT to help my home country of Lebanon. Since then, I haven't stopped thinking about my idea but I am in need of an experienced app developer to help make it a reality. If this peaked your interest and you are willing to work as co-founder please feel free to reach out.

contact email: ejje.marketplace@gmail.com
history.subject: Looking for experienced App Developer to help bring an idea to life
